<html>
<body>
<p>Reports duplicate bean names defined in the application context.</p>

<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code>
  &lt;beans profile="PROD"&gt;
    &lt;bean class="..." id="duplicatedName"/&gt;  &lt;!--  error --&gt;
    &lt;bean class="..." name="foo_name, duplicatedName"/&gt; &lt;!--  'duplicatedName' error --&gt;
    &lt;bean class="..." id="toBeAliased"/&gt;

    &lt;alias alias="duplicatedName" name="toBeAliased"/&gt; &lt;!--  'duplicatedName' error --&gt;
  &lt;/beans&gt;
</code></pre>
</body>
</html>
